<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>The Architecture of Frustration and Acceptance — Exhibition</title>
    <style>
      :root {
        --bg-color: #0a0a0a;
        --text-color: #f5f5f5;
        --text-muted: #888888;
        --border-color: #222222;
        --accent-color: #ffffff;
      }

      * {
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
        box-sizing: border-box;
      }
      body {
        background-color: var(--bg-color);
        color: var(--text-color);
        font-family:
          -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", Roboto, Helvetica,
          Arial, sans-serif;
        letter-spacing: -0.02em;
        -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
        padding: 8vw 5vw;
      }

      header {
        max-width: 1200px;
        margin: 0 auto 12vh auto;
      }
      .meta-info {
        display: flex;
        justify-content: space-between;
        font-size: 0.85rem;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        letter-spacing: 0.1em;
        color: var(--text-muted);
        border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-color);
        padding-bottom: 20px;
        margin-bottom: 30px;
      }
      h1 {
        font-size: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 3.5rem);
        font-weight: 400;
        line-height: 1.1;
        max-width: 800px;
      }

      .curatorial-statement {
        max-width: 800px;
        margin: 0 auto 15vh auto;
        font-size: clamp(1rem, 1.5vw, 1.2rem);
        line-height: 1.7;
        color: #ccc;
      }

      .project-section {
        max-width: 1200px;
        margin: 0 auto 18vh auto;
        border-top: 1px solid var(--border-color);
        padding-top: 40px;
      }
      .project-header {
        display: flex;
        justify-content: space-between;
        align-items: baseline;
        margin-bottom: 30px;
      }
      .project-title {
        font-size: clamp(1.5rem, 3vw, 2.2rem);
        font-weight: 400;
      }
      .project-num {
        font-family: monospace;
        color: var(--text-muted);
      }

      .media-wrapper {
        position: relative;
        width: 100%;
        background: #111111;
        border: 1px solid var(--border-color);
        margin-bottom: 40px;
        overflow: hidden;
        aspect-ratio: 16 / 9;
      }
      .media-wrapper iframe {
        position: absolute;
        top: 0;
        left: 0;
        width: 100%;
        height: 100%;
        border: none;
      }

      .project-content {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
        gap: 40px;
      }
      @media (min-width: 768px) {
        .project-content {
          grid-template-columns: 1fr 2fr;
        }
      }
      .content-sidebar h4 {
        font-size: 0.85rem;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        letter-spacing: 0.1em;
        color: var(--text-muted);
        margin-bottom: 10px;
      }
      .reflection-body {
        font-size: 1rem;
        line-height: 1.6;
        color: #dddddd;
      }
      .reflection-body p {
        margin-bottom: 20px;
      }

      .btn-action {
        display: inline-block;
        background: transparent;
        color: var(--accent-color);
        border: 1px solid var(--accent-color);
        padding: 12px 24px;
        font-size: 0.85rem;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        letter-spacing: 0.1em;
        text-decoration: none;
        transition: all 0.3s ease;
        margin-top: 15px;
      }
      .btn-action:hover {
        background: var(--accent-color);
        color: var(--bg-color);
      }

      .process-gallery {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(200px, 1fr));
        gap: 15px;
        margin-top: 30px;
      }
      .process-gallery img {
        width: 100%;
        height: auto;
        filter: grayscale(100%);
        opacity: 0.7;
        transition: all 0.3s ease;
        border: 1px solid var(--border-color);
      }
      .process-gallery img:hover {
        filter: grayscale(0%);
        opacity: 1;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <header>
      <div class="meta-info">
        <span>RMIT Digital Media Studio</span>
        <span>Assignment 4:Final Project Reflection</span>
      </div>
      <h1>这里<br />是标题</h1>
    </header>

    <main>
      <div class="curatorial-statement">
        <p>这里是引言。</p>
      </div>

      <section class="project-section">
        <div class="project-header">
          <h2 class="project-title">Day Dream</h2>
          <span class="project-num">I // WEB INTERACTIVE</span>
        </div>

        <div class="media-wrapper">
          <iframe
            src="https://animaeashe.github.io/Private/A1/"
            allow="autoplay"
          ></iframe>
        </div>

        <div class="project-content">
          <div class="content-sidebar">
            <h4>Dimensions</h4>
            <p style="color: var(--text-muted); font-size: 0.9rem">
              Web Based Interactive Work<br />HTML / CSS / JavaScript
            </p>
            <a
              href="https://animaeashe.github.io/Private/A1/"
              target="_blank"
              class="btn-action"
              >Open in New Tab</a
            >
          </div>
          <div class="reflection-body">
            <p>这里是作品介绍。</p>
            <p>这里是反思内容。</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="project-section">
        <div class="project-header">
          <h2 class="project-title">[NULL]</h2>
          <span class="project-num">II // UNITY WEBGL</span>
        </div>

        <div class="media-wrapper">
          <iframe
            frameborder="0"
            src="https://itch.io/embed-upload/17776201?color=333333"
            allowfullscreen=""
            width="1920"
            height="1080"
            ><a href="https://animaeashe.itch.io/null"
              >Play NULL on itch.io</a
            ></iframe
          >
        </div>

        <div class="project-content">
          <div class="content-sidebar">
            <h4>Dimensions</h4>
            <p style="color: var(--text-muted); font-size: 0.9rem">
              3D Digital Environment<br />Unity Engine / WebGL
            </p>
            <a
              href="https://yourname.itch.io/project2"
              target="_blank"
              class="btn-action"
              >View on itch.io</a
            >
          </div>
          <div class="reflection-body">
            <p>这里是作品介绍。</p>
            <p>这里是反思内容。</p>

            <div class="process-gallery">
              <img src="img.jpg" alt="Unity Process 1" />
              <img src="img.jpg" alt="Unity Process 2" />
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="project-section">
        <div class="project-header">
          <h2 class="project-title">Talk Back!!</h2>
          <span class="project-num">III // PERSUASIVE EXPERIMENT</span>
        </div>

        <div class="media-wrapper">
          <iframe
            src="https://itch.io/embed-upload/7654321?color=0a0a0a"
            allowfullscreen=""
            width="100%"
            height="100%"
            ><a href="https://yourname.itch.io/project3"
              >Play Talk Back!! on itch.io</a
            ></iframe
          >
        </div>

        <div class="project-content">
          <div class="content-sidebar">
            <h4>Dimensions</h4>
            <p style="color: var(--text-muted); font-size: 0.9rem">
              Narrative Solution<br />Unity Engine / Game Mechanics
            </p>
            <a
              href="https://yourname.itch.io/project3"
              target="_blank"
              class="btn-action"
              >View on itch.io</a
            >
          </div>
          <div class="reflection-body">
            <p>这里是作品介绍。</p>
            <p>这里是反思内容。</p>

            <div class="process-gallery">
              <img src="img.jpg" alt="Unity Process 3" />
              <img src="img.jpg" alt="Unity Process 4" />
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>
    </main>
  </body>
</html>
